    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The next time you make a ranged weapon attack during the spell's duration, the weapon's ammunition, or the weapon itself if it's a thrown weapon, transforms into a bolt of lightning. Make the attack roll as normal. The target takes [[/damage 4d8 type=lightning]] damage on a hit, or half as much damage on a miss, instead of the weapon's normal damage.</p><p>Whether you hit or miss, each creature within 10 feet of the target must make a Dexterity saving throw. Each of these creatures takes [[/damage 2d8 type=lightning]] damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><p>The piece of ammunition or weapon then returns to its normal form.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p></p><div data-roll-name-ancestor=\"At Higher Levels\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"1\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">At Higher Levels.</span></span> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, the damage for both effects of the spell increases by [[/damage 1d8]] for each slot level above 3rd.</p></div></div>",
      "chat": ""
    },
